parameters.text:
Prompt for Analyze Image

You are analyzing a weekly plan written in a notebook.

The page is divided into quadrants: Urgent / Not Urgent (columns) and Important / Not Important (rows).

Each bullet or phrase is an action item.

If an item is crossed out, mark it as finished = true. Otherwise, finished = false.

Return all items in structured JSON.

Output format:

{
  "quadrants": {
    "urgent_important": [
      {"task": "string", "finished": true|false},
      {"task": "string", "finished": true|false}
    ],
    "not_urgent_important": [
      {"task": "string", "finished": true|false}
    ],
    "urgent_not_important": [
      {"task": "string", "finished": true|false}
    ],
    "not_urgent_not_important": [
      {"task": "string", "finished": true|false}
    ]
  }
}


Rules:

Preserve original wording as much as possible.

If the quadrant placement is unclear, make your best guess.

Do not add commentary — output only the JSON.

